This is the main repo for my project located here: http://www.joepettersson.com/a-simple-jquery-image-slider/

If you have any problems feel free to file an issue here or contact me at the above link. Feel free to fork and add a pull request if necessary!

Description:
This is an implementation of one of Orman Clark's designs from Premium Pixels (http://www.premiumpixels.com/clean-simple-image-slider-psd/). 

